Package: jigsawR
Type: Package
Title: R Translations of JavaScript Jigsaw Puzzle Generators
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Philipp", "Thoss", , "ph.thoss@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4672-2792"))
Description: R translations of Draradech's JavaScript jigsaw puzzle generators
    with enhanced puzzle visualization capabilities. Supports rectangular,
    hexagonal, concentric, Voronoi, random shape, and SNIC superpixel puzzles
    with high-quality SVG output, gradient backgrounds, and configurable piece
    separation. Direct ports of the original JavaScript algorithms maintaining
    mathematical precision while adding R-based visualization, tessellation,
    and image-aware segmentation capabilities.
